<p class="Note">Abbreviation: CPG: clinical practice guideline</p></div></p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Clinical Algorithm(s)</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>The following algorithms are provided in the original guideline document:</p>
<ul style="list-style-type: disc;">
    <li>Module A: Determination of Appropriateness for Opioid Therapy </li>
    <li>Module B: Treatment with Opioid Therapy </li>
    <li>Module C: Tapering or Discontinuation of Opioid Therapy </li>
    <li>Module D: Patients Currently on Opioid Therapy </li>
</ul></div></p>

